Title: Center CB insulation tape 15mtr x 50mm x 3mm Black
Description: Supplied in a 15M length, this Center CB 50mm black elastomeric pipe insulation tape is made of closed cell insulation material with inbuilt Microban antimicrobial protection. Designed to insulate and control condensation, reducing energy losses and protecting against frost on pipes, air ducts, vessels and their fittings, this tape is suitable for use on hot and cold water services, chilled water lines, heating systems, air conditioning ductwork and refrigerated pipework.
